Interested NBER-affiliated researchers should contact Jean Roth, jroth@nber.org, for more information. Researchers not affiliated with the NBER may contact Satya Narain Singh, director of the Co-ordination & Publication Division at the NSSO, satyanarain.singh@gmail.com.
